sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    box #e0e7ff "Pod A (Frontend)"
    participant AppA as Application Container
    participant KernelA as iptables (Kernel)
    participant EnvoyA as Envoy Sidecar
    end
    
    box #f1f5f9 "Pod B (Backend)"
    participant EnvoyB as Envoy Sidecar
    participant KernelB as iptables (Kernel)
    participant AppB as Application Container
    end

    AppA->>KernelA: HTTP request to backend-svc:80
    KernelA->>EnvoyA: Redirect to local loopback port 15001
    EnvoyA->>EnvoyA: xDS lookup; selects Pod B IP & encapsulates in mTLS
    EnvoyA->>EnvoyB: TCP connection on port 15008 (mTLS tunnel)
    EnvoyB->>EnvoyB: TLS decrypt; checks AuthorizationPolicy
    EnvoyB->>KernelB: Forwards HTTP request to localhost:80
    KernelB->>AppB: Redirects socket to App socket listener
    AppB-->>KernelB: Response 200 OK
    KernelB-->>EnvoyB: localhost loopback
    EnvoyB-->>EnvoyA: Encrypted response tunnel
    EnvoyA-->>KernelA: Decrypts & returns response
    KernelA-->>AppA: Delivers response data
